data.description: TIS THE SEASON, RATES ARE DOWN!  Would you like to start with a $2000 lower interest rate or perhaps a $1500 Lender Credit ?  Both could be available and will be applied towards the buyer's closing costsand pre-paids if the buyer chooses to use the seller's preferred lender. This credit is inaddition to any negotiated seller concessions.  OR perhaps you are a VETERAN AND WOULD LIKE TO ASSUME A LOW RATE??OPEN ONE LEVEL FLOOR PLAN + BONUS over the two-car garage; makes this 1-1/2 Story the ideal home for you!  Why wait to build when you can score today on this well-kept home?  Roomy with over 2,000 sqft of modern living.  Enter the foyer and notice popular luxury vinyl flooring that runs through all high traffic living spaces.Great light dances in the formal dining room ''flexspace'' and bouncing off the vaulted ceiling immediately to your right upon entering this home.  This space could also provide you with a home office or another living area.  The chef's deli opens to the spacious great room with high vaulted ceiling and lots of natural light. The "super-size" owner's "suite retreat," tucked into the back of home, has dual closets and trey ceilings with bath ensuite including double vanity sinks, separate shower and garden soaking tub, that everyone wants! The covered patio space leads to the large fenced backyard with plenty of room for BBQ's or outdoor play.  Two additional bedrooms on the first level are split from the master with adjoining full bath with laundry room close by. The 4th bedroom/bonus room over the garage is the perfect multi-purpose space for roommates, growing teens, office space or a movie room. Other upgrades included: upgraded lightning and plumbing fixtures, tankless water heater, wood fence, programmable thermostats, architectural shingles, new stainless steel refrigerator and remaining builder warranties convey with sale.    Foxbank Plantation is a master planned community inclusive of shops, schools, churches and amenities. There is a 67 acre lake with a dock, fishing and kayaking; 16 ponds, protected wetlands, two swimming pools, fitness center, children's play area, park-like community spaces, dog park, great lawn with pavilion overlooking the lake, etc....  See the floorplan under documents and don't miss the 360 degree video walk-through to see all the interior details of this lovely home.  PREPARE to be excited, run to the phone and schedule your private tour today before it is too late.
